 # Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [Unreleased]


## [0.0.1] - 2019-09-23
### Added
- First release

## [0.0.2] - 2019-10-02
### Added
- a mirror option, so a non-symmetrical wing can be defined
- a new panel attribute "loc_slope" to store the panel local slope
- tests for geometry, vortices, airfoil and vlm modules. Validation tests from Bertin & Smith reference for AIC, gamma and CL calculation

### Changed
- renamed the "add_wing" method to "add_surface". Moved the calculation of the AIC matrix and the leading edge input check to the "add_surface" method
- renamed the "check_mesh" method to "show_mesh"
- renamed "camber_gradient" to "camber_slope"
- overall code readability, to make it look more pythonic and less matlabic. Improved plotting

### Removed
- script versions of the examples (pilatusPC12, airfoils, mesh and vortex)
